<%= image_tag "logo3.png", :width => "204", :height => "106", class: "mommylogo" %>

<div class="profile-wrapper animated fadeIn">
  <div class="profile">
    <h2 class="page-title"><%= "#{@user.first_name} #{@user.last_name} History " %></h2>

    <% if current_user.mother == false %>
    <%= link_to "Go back to #{@user.first_name}'s Profile", user_path(@user.id), class: "mom-btn" %>
    <% else %>
    <%= link_to "Go back to My Profile", user_path(@user.id), class: "mom-btn" %>
    <% end %>

    <% if @user.mother == true %>
      <% if @user.tri_1_1 != nil && @user.tri_1_2 != nil && @user.tri_1_3 != nil %>
      <div class="stage1">
        <div class="tri-title">
            <%= image_tag "blue-heart.png", :width => "55", :height => "70" %>

            <h3 class="page-title">First Trimester</h3>
        </div>

            <p>
              1. Are you having any cramps or pain?
                <ul><li><%= @user.tri_1_1 %></li></ul>
            </p>

            <p>
              2. Do you feel feverish with a very high body temperature?
                <ul><li><%= @user.tri_1_2 %></li></ul>
            </p>

            <p>
              3. Are you having excessive nausea and vomitting?
              <ul><li><%= @user.tri_1_3 %></li></ul>
            </p>

          <br/>

            <h4 class="page-title">Comments:</h4>
              <div class="comment1">
                  <% @comments.each do |comment| %>
                    <% if comment.trimester_id == 1 %>
                       <% if comment.doctor_id == nil %>
                      <div class="mom-cmnt">
                        <%= image_tag "pregnancy-with-hearts(1)copy.png", :width => "50", :height => "70", class: "mini-mom" %>
                          <div class="mom-cmnt2">
                              <p class="mom"><%= "#{@user.first_name}:" %></p>
                              <p class="comnt"><%= comment.comment %></p>
                              <p class="time"><%= comment.created_at.in_time_zone('Eastern Time (US & Canada)').to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %></p>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                      <%else%>
                      <div class="doc-cmnt">
                        <%= image_tag "steth-icon.png", :width => "50", :height => "70", class: "mini-doc" %>
                         <div class="doc-comnt2">
                            <p class="doc"><%= "#{@doctor.first_name}:" %></p>
                            <p class="comnt"><%= comment.comment %></p>
                            <p class="time"><%= comment.created_at.in_time_zone('Eastern Time (US & Canada)').to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %></p>
                         </div>
                      </div>

                      <% end %>
                    <% end %>
                  <% end %>
              </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>

      <br/>

      <% if @user.tri_2_1 != nil && @user.tri_2_2 != nil && @user.tri_2_3 != nil %>
      <div class="stage2">

        <div class="tri-title">
          <%= image_tag "blue-heart.png", :width => "55", :height => "70" %>
          <h3 class="page-title">Second Trimester</h3>
        </div>

          <p>
            1. Are you having an increase pelvic pressure and/or unusual discharge, eg. bleeding?
              <ul><li><%= @user.tri_2_1 %></li></ul>
          </p>

          <p>
            2. Are you having headaches that are not relieved with over-the-counter
            medications or have visual changes associated with them, persistent vomiting, and upper abdominal pain?
              <ul><li><%= @user.tri_2_2 %></li></ul>
          </p>

          <p>
            3. Do any of these symptoms apply to you? Vaginal pressure, Low-back pain, Frequent urination, Diarrhea, Increased vaginal discharge, Tightness in the lower abdomen
            <ul><li><%= @user.tri_2_3 %></li></ul>
          </p>

          <br>

          <h4 class="page-title">Comments:</h4>
            <div class="comment1">
                <% @comments.each do |comment| %>
                  <% if comment.trimester_id == 2 %>
                     <% if comment.doctor_id == nil %>
                     <div class="mom-cmnt">
                       <%= image_tag "pregnancy-with-hearts(1)copy.png", :width => "50", :height => "70", class: "mini-mom" %>
                         <div class="mom-cmnt2">
                             <p class="mom"><%= "#{@user.first_name}:" %></p>
                             <p class="comnt"><%= comment.comment %></p>
                             <p class="time"><%= comment.created_at.in_time_zone('Eastern Time (US & Canada)').to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %></p>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                       <%else%>
                     <div class="doc-cmnt">
                       <%= image_tag "steth-icon.png", :width => "50", :height => "70", class: "mini-doc" %>
                        <div class="doc-comnt2">
                           <p class="doc"><%= "#{@doctor.first_name}:" %></p>
                           <p class="comnt"><%= comment.comment %></p>
                           <p class="time"><%= comment.created_at.in_time_zone('Eastern Time (US & Canada)').to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %></p>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <% end %>
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
            </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>

      <br/>

      <% if @user.tri_3_1 != nil && @user.tri_3_2 != nil && @user.tri_3_3 != nil %>
      <div class="stage3">
        <div class="tri-title">
          <%= image_tag "blue-heart.png", :width => "55", :height => "70" %>
          <h3 class="page-title">Third Trimester</h3>
        </div>

        <p>
          1. Are you having headaches that are not relieved with over-the-counter
          medications or have visual changes associated with them, persistent vomiting,
          and upper abdominal pain?
            <ul><li><%= @user.tri_3_1 %></li></ul>
        </p>

        <p>
          2. Is there decreased movement from your baby?
            <ul><li><%= @user.tri_3_2 %></li></ul>
        </p>

        <p>
          3. Do any of these changes apply to you?  Vaginal discharge to a pink or
         reddish color, menstrual-like cramps, pressure in your pelvis or lower abdomen,
         and contractions that last for at least an hour that arenâ€™t Braxton Hicks contractions.
            <ul><li><%= @user.tri_3_3 %></li></ul>
        </p>

      <br/>

        <h4 class="page-title">Comments:</h4>
          <div class="comment1">
              <% @comments.each do |comment| %>
                <% if comment.trimester_id == 3 %>
                   <% if comment.doctor_id == nil %>
                   <div class="mom-cmnt">
                       <%= image_tag "pregnancy-with-hearts(1)copy.png", :width => "50", :height => "70", class: "mini-mom" %>
                         <div class="mom-cmnt2">
                             <p class="mom"><%= "#{@user.first_name}:" %></p>
                             <p class="comnt"><%= comment.comment %></p>
                             <p class="time"><%= comment.created_at.in_time_zone('Eastern Time (US & Canada)').to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %></p>
                         </div>
                   </div>
                     <%else%>
                   <div class="doc-cmnt">
                     <%= image_tag "steth-icon.png", :width => "50", :height => "70", class: "mini-doc" %>
                      <div class="doc-comnt2">
                         <p class="doc"><%= "#{@doctor.first_name}:" %></p>
                         <p class="comnt"><%= comment.comment %></p>
                         <p class="time"><%= comment.created_at.in_time_zone('Eastern Time (US & Canada)').to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %></p>
                      </div>
                   </div>
                   <% end %>
                <% end %>
              <% end %>
          </div>

      </div>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
